data.description: Back on the market! Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in the heart of Redlands. This beautiful residence offers a spacious living room and great floor plan for families. The open concept dining area is ideal for entertaining, while the cozy living room provides a relaxing retreat with a fireplace. Enjoy the convenience of a two car garage with plenty of parking. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is close to schools, parks and all the amenities Redlands has to offer. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this house your new home!
